These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: skydiving, puzzles
Job: entrepreneur, journalist
1. Job:entrepreneur is in an even position##4
2. Job:journalist == Hobby:puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | skydiving |
| Job     | journalist    | entrepreneur   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: hot-chocolate, mirinda
Sport: volleyball, surfing
1. Sport:volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:mirinda is on the left of Beverage:hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate        |
| Sport      | volleyball  | surfing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
